1
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:37,640
Old Chen, are you okay?

2
00:00:40,799 --> 00:00:41,479
Get up.

3
00:00:41,479 --> 00:00:42,520
Come on, get up.

4
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:13,920
The treasure you sought your whole life,

5
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,159
in an instant,

6
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,760
has been destroyed.

7
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,799
Uncle Min, I want to ask you now,

8
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,439
at this very moment,

9
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:24,359
how does it feel?

10
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:32,159
All for a single stone,

11
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,079
Lingla's heart,

12
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,359
her life,

13
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,359
in your eyes,

14
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,040
were worth nothing.

15
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,719
And you killed her with your own hands.

16
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,760
Everything I've done today

17
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,799
was to show you

18
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,599
what it means to lose the one you love.

19
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,799
Losing the one you love,

20
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,319
how exactly does it feel?

21
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,079
Godfather!

22
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,480
An Xiang!

23
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,040
Stay back!

24
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:05,079
Bi Huaqiang,

25
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,240
before the Lingxiao Pearl,

26
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,840
nothing else matters.

27
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,639
I...

28
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:24,240
Actually, I...

29
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,800
I knew everything.

30
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:30,439
I knew it all.

31
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,319
It's just that

32
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:36,080
even now, you still

33
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,800
don't understand this truth.

34
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,479
Why?

35
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,599
Why am I always one step short?

36
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,400
Why?

37
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:10,199
From Yunling to Nanyun,

38
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,639
and now to here,

39
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:16,560
the relics and artifacts we've seen

40
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,319
are things other archaeologists might never

41
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,600
experience in their entire lives.

42
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,160
So the Lingxiao Pearl shattered. Let it.

43
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:31,160
Having you with me through it all,

44
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:37,879
it was all worth it.

45
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,240
Don't cry.

46
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:47,360
Only time and the universe are eternal.

47
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,040
Shutong!

48
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:01,240
We're on Beijing time,

49
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,759
but here it's 80 degrees east longitude.

50
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,560
The time difference is 2 hours 40 minutes.

51
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:09,439
The time engraved up there is right now.

52
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,319
It's now!

53
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,759
The Lingxiao Pearl!

54
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,240
That is the real Lingxiao Pearl!

55
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,639
This... this is truly...

56
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,600
fate!

57
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,560
This is what you call fate!

58
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:14,879
Don't move!

59
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:16,800
An Xiang!

60
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,560
Godfather!

61
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
Get back here!

62
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,079
What are you doing?

63
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:22,240
What am I doing?

64
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,800
I've hated the sight of you for ages.

65
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:24,920
Stay still.

66
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,800
In their historical records,

67
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,959
this eye pattern has appeared.

68
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,240
Millennia ago in the Western Regions,

69
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:06,199
people used Kali-Ganga human sacrifices

70
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:07,800
to perform resurrection rituals.

71
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,000
It's said the Lingxiao Pearl

72
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,279
holds secrets about the universe.

73
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:20,319
I just want, in my lifetime,

74
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,040
to see this Lingxiao Pearl

75
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,600
and see if it's truly as legends say.

76
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:28,759
Since young, I was trained like a machine,

77
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,079
all to find the Lingxiao Pearl.

78
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:33,519
Believe me, my lifelong pursuit

79
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:35,560
is only to know what secret

80
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,560
the Lingxiao Pearl conceals.

81
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:40,160
If this Pearl can resurrect a princess,

82
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,279
it can definitely save Chen Youxi's life.

83
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:50,759
Lingxiao Pearl!

84
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,399
Chen Youxi!

85
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,439
Old Chen!

86
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,879
He passed out again?

87
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:58,199
Officer He, he won't make it this time!

88
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:59,879
Quick, give him CPR!

89
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,720
Chen Youxi!

90
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:06,680
Chen Youxi!

91
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,120
How are you feeling?

92
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,000
What are you doing?

93
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,600
Want me to give you mouth-to-mouth too?

94
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:20,639
No thanks.

95
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,720
How are you feeling now?

96
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,240
Why so serious?

97
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,439
It's not the first time I've passed out.

98
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,519
After you passed out just now,

99
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,320
did you feel anything else?

100
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,919
I dreamed of the old Mengna Valley.

101
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:51,080
All beings suffer,

102
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:59,840
the world is a prison.

103
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:09,480
When the three lamps shine bright,

104
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:16,240
all suffering shall pass.

105
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,759
Blessed by the divine pearl,

106
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:44,879
Mengna Valley will last forever.

107
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,120
You mean

108
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,320
that the ceremony in Mengna Valley

109
00:11:51,519 --> 00:11:53,120
triggered the Lingxiao Pearl's energy?

110
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,080
And the destruction of Mengna Valley

111
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:57,200
was caused by the impact of energy waves?

112
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:01,600
That doesn't sound very scientific.

113
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,320
Didn't you say

114
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:07,799
the Lingxiao Pearl is highly magnetic?

115
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,120
Could that be the reason?

116
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:12,600
Even if it has a strong magnetic field,

117
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,000
it didn't just appear out of nowhere.

118
00:12:14,679 --> 00:12:16,159
How could it instantly

119
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:17,639
destroy the entire Mengna Valley?

120
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:18,919
Then could it be

121
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,360
because of the cave they were in?

122
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:24,399
This cave is very enclosed.

123
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,279
Could the air contain some substance

124
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,360
that made them hallucinate?

125
00:12:30,039 --> 00:12:30,879
I'm not sure.

126
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:32,480
But do you guys remember

127
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,960
when I was at the Dian King's ruins,

128
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,919
exposed to the Lingxiao Pearl's magnetism,

129
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,919
my brain simulated the situation at the time?

130
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,720
Of course I remember.

131
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,480
Wasn't Lu's star student, Ding Dawei,

132
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,799
exposed in the exact same way?

133
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,200
Stop bringing it up.

134
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:46,799
Are you saying

135
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,399
that the dream you just had

136
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,919
could also be a simulation?

137
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,480
I can't rule out that possibility.

138
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,399
If the Lingxiao Pearl really poses

139
00:12:54,399 --> 00:12:55,919
unpredictable dangers,

140
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:57,039
then the best thing to do

141
00:12:57,039 --> 00:12:58,919
is to let the professionals study it.

142
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,399
Well, aren't you noble.

143
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,679
But we still have a guy tied up here

144
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:07,360
who came just for the Lingxiao Pearl.

145
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,000
What do we do about him?

146
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,440
Take him with us.

147
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:11,240
You got it.

148
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,039
Shutong,

149
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,200
copy the text and patterns up there.

150
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,720
Old Lu, pack up your things too. Hurry.

151
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,480
Fatty,

152
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,559
I'm leaving Uncle Min to you.

153
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:22,960
I'll go up and document this.

154
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:23,720
Alright.

155
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,480
Brother Chen,

156
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,080
are you just going to leave like this?

157
00:13:28,639 --> 00:13:30,759
I'm here to explore Mengna Valley's past.

158
00:13:30,759 --> 00:13:32,320
I've reached the end of the line.

159
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:33,840
It's time for me to report back.

160
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,840
What about everyone else?

161
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,159
Do you all think the same?

162
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,399
We...

163
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:43,039
Let me tell you,

164
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,960
we listen to Commander Chen, of course.

165
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:49,159
It's perfectly fine for you

166
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:51,120
to protect historical relics.

167
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:52,840
But don't forget,

168
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:55,039
Brother Chen's life and mine

169
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:57,600
are both tied to this Lingxiao Pearl.

170
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:01,159
Miss He, my death doesn't matter,

171
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:03,039
but don't you care about

172
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,399
Brother Chen's life?

173
00:14:10,559 --> 00:14:11,360
First of all,

174
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,200
this Lingxiao Pearl

175
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:16,000
was discovered in the PRC.

176
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:17,679
It's protected by the state

177
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:18,879
and should be handed over to the state.

178
00:14:19,679 --> 00:14:20,480
Second,

179
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:21,799
whether this Lingxiao Pearl

180
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:23,759
actually affects Chen Youxi's illness

181
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,879
can only be determined after

182
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:26,799
professionals have studied it.

183
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,159
Third,

184
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:32,279
based on our past experience,

185
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:34,200
touching the Lingxiao Pearl

186
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,720
will trigger a chain of disasters.

187
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:37,960
So this time,

188
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,919
we must learn from our mistakes.

189
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:41,399
Lastly,

190
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,759
in every past disaster,

191
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,360
the Lingxiao Pearl is often lost.

192
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,919
Therefore,

193
00:14:47,919 --> 00:14:49,279
if you truly believe

194
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,080
that this Lingxiao Pearl

195
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,200
is your only hope of survival,

196
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:55,600
then you should rationally leave it here.

197
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,600
Once we get out,

198
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,840
we'll report it to the authorities

199
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,759
and have professional exploration experts

200
00:15:01,799 --> 00:15:03,279
to come take it back for research.

201
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,679
Look at Officer He's sense of duty.

202
00:15:10,879 --> 00:15:12,000
Well said.

203
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,000
You become who you hang out with.

204
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,279
You should learn from her.

205
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:15,600
Alright.

206
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,039
Get ready to head out.

207
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:17,960
Got it.

208
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,080
So, how about it?

209
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:26,720
Mind at ease now?

210
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:27,799
I've given up.

211
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:31,159
Off we go!

212
00:15:33,279 --> 00:15:33,960
An Xiang.

213
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,039
Nobody move!

214
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,799
I've got your godfather right here.

215
00:15:37,919 --> 00:15:39,720
I dare you to touch my godfather.

216
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:40,759
Throw your weapons over here.

217
00:15:40,799 --> 00:15:41,799
Let my godfather go.

218
00:15:41,799 --> 00:15:43,080
An Xiang, don't do anything rash.

219
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:43,919
Put the knife down.

220
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:45,120
Put the knife down.

221
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,200
You toss your weapons over first.

222
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,639
You little brat.

223
00:15:49,639 --> 00:15:51,320
Wanna bet I'll kill him right now?

224
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,600
Throw your weapons over here!

225
00:15:52,639 --> 00:15:53,679
Or I'll kill him.

226
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,320
You, you, you...
